title: 2010.10.03-MotoGP.15.Japan.Race.BBC1_UK [TDMK1]
description:
2010.10.03-MotoGP.15.Japan.Race.BBC1_UK-TDMK1.m4v

The Japanese Grand Prix. Jennie Gow introduces coverage from the Twin Ring circuit in Motegi, where the 14th round of the season takes place. Jorge Lorenzo won this race last year and the Spaniard holds an impressive lead in the standings heading into this year's meeting. With commentary by Steve Parrish and Charlie Cox.

Now encoded as 'MP4 All Play'... As a departure from the DivX files which I have uploaded in the past, I've made the decision to get with the 21st century & start encoding with the following specs this year;

MP4 - 640x352 - 800Kb/s H264 Video - 44.1KHz/128Kbps Stereo AAC Audio

My belief is this is the best all round setup, and hopefully you will agree!

This video will play on a computer with VLC, XBMC, XBox360, PS3, iPad all iPhones - enjoy the show... :)
